details.name: Battle Trance
details.description: Troll unleashes a powerful battle trance, that forces you to continuously attack the closest enemy unit within 900 range, prioritizing heroes. Damage does not kill you during this mode. Grants you bonus lifesteal, attack speed and movement speed. Applies a Basic Dispel. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Reduces Battle Trance cooldown and allows it to be cast on allied or enemy heroes. Lasts half duration on enemies.
